840
00:56:57.574 --> 00:56:58.658
Prague.

841
00:57:01.328 --> 00:57:03.914
Well... Yeah.

842
00:57:04.956 --> 00:57:05.999
Tell me something...

843
00:57:08.502 --> 00:57:09.920
Do you ever think
