882
00:59:59.798 --> 01:00:02.300
We work harder.

883
01:00:02.300 --> 01:00:05.845
Instead of standing here
wringing our hands in despair.

884
01:00:05.845 --> 01:00:07.430
We need more trains.

885
01:00:07.430 --> 01:00:09.641
